      "body": "Optimize `asyncio.all_tasks()` for the common case where the event loop is running in the current thread by avoiding stop-the-world pauses and locking.\n\nThis optimization is already present for `asyncio.current_task()` so we do the same for `asyncio.all_tasks()`.\n(cherry picked from commit 95e5d596308620acbd860ec25a40ef95c2b62eaa)\n\nCo-authored-by: Kumar Aditya <kumaraditya@python.org>\n\n<!-- gh-issue-number: gh-140414 -->\n* Issue: gh-140414\n<!-- /gh-issue-number -->\n",
